---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 bg-[#F7F8F4]">
    <div
        class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start mb-12 gap-8"
    >
        <h2
            class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 leading-[1.1]"
        >
            Clean & Simple <br /> Design Strong Results.
        </h2>
        <div class="max-w-md">
            <p class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-snug">
                Hey, I’m Masjidul, A Digital Designer Focused On Simple, Smart,
                And Intentional Design That Actually Works.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start">
        <div class="md:col-span-5">
            <Image
                src="/masjidul.png"
                height={600}
                width={600}
                alt="Masjidul - Digital Designer"
                class="rounded-2xl w-full object-cover shadow-sm"
            />
        </div>

        <div class="md:col-span-7 flex flex-col gap-6">
            <span
                class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 border border-gray-400 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold w-fit text-gray-800"
            >
                About Me
            </span>

            <div
                class="space-y-6 text-lg font-medium text-gray-800 leading-relaxed"
            >
                <p>
                    With 4 Years Of Experience As A UI/UX Designer, I Don’t Just
                    Build Interfaces; I Build Engines For Digital Success. My
                    Approach Combines Deep Empathy For The User With A Sharp
                    Focus On Business Objectives, Specializing In SaaS,
                    E-Commerce, And High-Growth Startup Ecosystems.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Throughout My Career—Collaborating With Forward-Thinking
                    Teams Like Signature Park And AdSession.Uk—I’ve Learned That
                    The Best Designs Are The Ones That Disappear, Leaving Only A
                    Seamless Experience For The User And Tangible ROI For The
                    Stakeholder.
                </p>

                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <p>
                        <span class="block text-gray-900"
                            >Why Work With Me?</span
                        >
                        Proven Impact: Helped Clients Like Reshom And AJA International
                        Achieve A 10% Growth Post-Redesign.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Versatile Expertise: From Complex SaaS Dashboards To
                        Sleek Portfolio Sites.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Strategic Partnership: I Act As A Consultant For Your
                        Brand, Ensuring Every Pixel Serves A Purpose In The
                        Digital Landscape.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
